  "abc: 0" , "abc: 1"
])

const amenRoll    = pat => iter(8, fast(16, pat))
const amenGlitch  = pat => pat.degradedBy(0.9).chop(32)
const amenReverse = par => pat.sometimesBy(0.4, p=> p.rev())

  amenChop(
    pat
      .sometimesBy(0.2, p => amenRoll(p))
      .sometimesBy(0.4, p => amenGlitch(p))
      .sometimesBy(0.8, p=> amenReverse(p))
  )

    .room(0.3)
    .size(0.8)
    .crush(10)
    .gain(1.1)

  .cut(1)
  .lpf(6000)
  .hpf(20)
  .pan(sine.slow(4).range(0,1))

amenRoom(amenFX(base))

hush()
